n style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以「不排除」三個字係非常重要<br />\n</span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:45:31.000Z","msg":"[緊急! 突發! 得返唔夠48小時!] (熱門仲係一個文宣Post都冇)721 全港最大型既線上文宣圖庫第二彈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332279</a><br />\n<br />\n唔理衝唔衝 721金鍾<br />\n推到上熱門"},{"pid":"9e130e9b6e2bb8637ec395c8b3a1ead1f7a36324","tid":1331693,"uid":92585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"721 新時代"},{"pid":"8c7db01dc342ec1d9b33045c78816064f5c69c01","tid":1331693,"uid":198634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0eba740a8855790ccc04c25d0e028f5c1740df0","tid":1331693,"uid":266190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:49:11.000Z","msg":"推 「7&middot;21 見」"},{"pid":"941514ffb1817fad5605f9665c560a85587e7bd6","tid":1331693,"uid":166708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />強帖留名"},{"pid":"fe92d3d079f0778b1c593e25fc3be45b9e72d942","tid":1331693,"uid":259812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"一國兩制 係西方國家支持你嘅前提<br />\n唔係佢地唔想支持香港<br />\n<br />\n係支持你香港成立<span style=\"color: red;\">臨時政府</span><br />\n等同同中國敵對關係<br />\n<br />\n邊個敢支持，咁仲唔係趕客？<br />\n<br />\n臨時立會合理好多"},{"pid":"5699e9f528c8a7fd842a53f2093d21ff17c9345b","tid":1331693,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"臨時立法會又好似真係比臨時政府易做,立法會代表唔到民意呢樣應該全香港都認同,之前71又拆左個無代表性既立法會。<br />\n不過要成立臨時立法會既話要有足夠認受性,好似之前立法會唔記得邊個委員會,班保皇黨唔滿意泛民拉布自己立左另一個人做主席。然後同一時間開會,出現左有兩個主席既衝突。<br />\n如果要搞臨時立法會,一定會有類似既衝突令全香港知道有臨時立法會。只係宣佈成立係唔夠,因為媒體唔會幫你報,71衝完立會都無人記得金鐘宣言。"},{"pid":"b961b10459735fb790a63784ca62ea4737a2ab59","tid":1331693,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981ccba23eb12d5da0898a9b898f25f5d5ed705e","tid":1331693,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:06:58.000Z","msg":"ok, 唔行一步都要行半步"},{"pid":"681ae443349526088b1169f5d33f0084a4f14eac","tid":1331693,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7dc61076c4e7f23a47c96aaa44ec281b6b7f2627","tid":1331693,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe92d3d079f0778b1c593e25fc3be45b9e72d942","tid":1331693,"uid":259812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"一國兩制 係西方國家支持你嘅前提<br />\n唔係佢地唔想支持香港<br />\n<br />\n係支持你香港成立<span style=\"color: red;\">臨時政府</span><br />\n等同同中國敵對關係<br />\n<br />\n邊個敢支持，咁仲唔係趕客？<br />\n<br />\n臨時立會合理好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"我補充少少 我覺得臨時政府成立大前提係要<br />\n國際社會公認<span style=\"color: red;\">一國兩制完全被破壞</span><br />\n到時就..."},{"pid":"518d7dc27234ad1efd90b1b4711ef2c281e10cb0","tid":1331693,"uid":138144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:09:11.000Z","msg":"721見"},{"pid":"c605ffdcaaa7b9ce523dd934912862e9659c450f","tid":1331693,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"呢一個做法比較可取<br />\n反正香港人都唔係個個都知<br />\n就麻煩共產黨宣傳下<img 